# Frontend work

Follow @docs/Reference/engineering/development/FRONTEND_STANDARDS.md and @docs/Reference/engineering/architecture/FRONTEND_ARCHITECTURE.md.

- Use the patterns in @docs/Reference/engineering/development/FRONTEND_RECIPES.md; mirror a nearby component over improvising.
- Consume the API strictly per @docs/Reference/engineering/architecture/CONTRACTS.md (don't assume a response shape).
- Before "done": run the gate in @docs/Reference/engineering/development/DEFINITION_OF_DONE_FRONTEND.md.
